---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Fingriffin">
  <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem;">
    
    <h1>About Fingriffin</h1>

    <p>
      Fingriffin is a journal about investing, entrepreneurship,
      business finance, and financial decision-making.
    </p>

    <p>
      The goal is not to provide stock tips or market predictions.
      Instead, Fingriffin focuses on frameworks, lessons, and
      observations gathered from years of investing, managing
      capital, building businesses, and learning from mistakes.
    </p>

    <p>
      Every article combines experience, analysis, and practical
      takeaways that readers can apply to their own financial lives.
    </p>

    <a href="/">← Home</a>

  </main>
</Layout>